:: BlasesLoaded

[[Blases Loaded|https://blases-loaded.sibr.dev/#/tabs/about]] shows games in progress in a format that may feel familiar to those who follow baseball, with native mobile support. It's brought to you by RangerRick.

Get the [[iOS app|https://apps.apple.com/us/app/id1529695719]] or [[Android app|https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.raccoonfink.blobile]] if those are relevant to you!

Source code, links to beta builds, and issue tracking [[here|https://github.com/RangerRick/blobile]]. Discussion of this project happens at @@.channel;#blases-loaded@@ under 'Major Projects'.